  "text": "The networking of different stakeholders within the tourism sector can assist SMMEs in encouraging collective promotion of tourism products and overcoming issues that are the result of competition [CITATION_1] . When it comes to managing competitiveness of tourism, the role of networking, especially externally, should be highlighted.",
